  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>This is a unique variation of the <strong>Fire Release: Hot Sun</strong> Jutsu, where you create 8 smaller ruby red spheres of Fire in the air and have them float midair no higher than 30 feet and no further than 120 feet from you. As a Bonus action on your turn, you may command a single sphere to attack a single creature. Make a Ninjutsu attack against a single creature. On a hit they take 4d8+4 Fire damage and the sphere is lost. If you miss you still lose one of the Fire spheres.</p>",
